&lt;h4&gt;Location: The Senior Platform Partnership Business Development Manager is a remote, work-from-home role, as are all positions at Acceleration Partners. Some travel is required for client meetings, internal meetings, conferences, and other events.&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;h4&gt;THE ROLE:&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Acceleration Partners is hiring a Senior Platform Partnership Business Development Manager to own and grow platform and API partnerships that drive SMB advertiser acquisition and revenue at scale for our client, TikTok For Business. This role will sit at the intersection of product, engineering, and go-to-market: structuring deals, deepening technical integrations, and accelerating how partners bring TikTok For Business to their merchants and clients. API knowledge will be a huge advantage for this role.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The most critical phase of this role spans from initial business development through complete partner onboarding and integration. That means the ideal candidate is a true hunter: someone who can identify and close new partnership opportunities and then drive them all the way through to live, operational integrations. We’re looking for a fast learner with commercial instincts and the technical curiosity to bridge the gap between business development and engineering.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h4&gt;TOP 5 JOB RESPONSIBILITIES:&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;u&gt;PARTNERSHIP BUSINESS DEVELOPMENT&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/strong&gt; - Identifies, pursues, and closes new platform and API partnerships with CRM platforms, e-commerce tools, and marketing automation providers. Owns the full BD cycle from first contact through signed agreement. Builds and maintains a strong network across the platform partnership ecosystem and represents TikTok For Business at senior and C-level engagements.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;u&gt;PARTNER ONBOARDING AND INTEGRATION&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/strong&gt; - Drives the critical post-close phase: shepherding partners through technical onboarding, scoping API integration requirements, and working closely with product and engineering teams to get integrations live. Translates commercial commitments into operational reality, ensuring partners can activate advertisers at scale via TikTok For Business APIs.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;u&gt;JOINT GO-TO-MARKET EXECUTION&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/strong&gt; - Co-creates and executes co-marketing, co-selling, and activation programs with partners to drive advertiser onboarding. Builds joint GTM motions that connect TikTok platform strengths to each partner’s merchant or client base, with the goal of growing effective monthly active advertiser (EMAA) counts.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;u&gt;PERFORMANCE OWNERSHIP AND REPORTING&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/strong&gt; - Tracks and owns partnership KPIs including registrations, new customer acquisition (NCA), EMAA, and revenue. Uses data to identify what is working, what isn’t and where to focus energy. Brings a structured, analytical approach to optimization across a portfolio of partnerships.&lt;/p&gt;
